Class LongArrayArray

          • com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.primitive.array.arrays.LongArrayArray
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.esotericsoftware.kryo.KryoSerializable, Initializable, NamedObject, Countable, Sized, CompressibleCollection
    public final class LongArrayArray
extends PrimitiveArrayArray
    Optimized storage of two dimensional long arrays. A sequence of LongArray objects can be added by calling add(LongIterable). The stored array can be retrieved later by calling get(int) passing in the identifier that was returned by add. The number of long arrays can be retrieved with size()

    This class supports the hashCode() / equals(Object) contract and is KryoSerializable

    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
    See Also:
    LongIterable, LongIterator, LongArray, KryoSerializable
